fields.name: ||Starting Weapon||
fields.value: ||Starts with **Peachone** and **Ebony wings** that do not show in the weapon slots.||

fields.name: ||Ability||
fields.value: ||Gains +1 Recovery and +1% Luck every level. Gains +1 Revival every 100 levels. Has hidden weapons.||

fields.name: ||Unlock||
fields.value: ||Go to the balcony in **Cappella Magna** below where the NFT spawns, while having both **Peachone** and **Ebony wings** on a character without golden eggs.||
